title: Khaidi No. 150
subTitle: After escaping from prison, a criminal flees the country. Having spent his entire life on the wrong side of the law, he is suddenly move by the plight of farmers he meets there and fights for their cause.

title: Raaz Rangon Ka
subTitle: A teacher, smitten student and struggling filmmaker become entangled in the search for a missing teen. Their quest reveals hidden truths that threaten to upend lives.

title: Ek Zakhmi Romeo
subTitle: Ananya loves her best friend, Surya, while he falls for another woman, Pooja. However, after his heartbreak, Surya is too late to realise who truly loved him as Ananya rejects him.

title: Bharaate
subTitle: Jagan, a local travel guide, falls in love with Radha, a tourist who visits his city. Though she leaves without saying goodbye, fate conspires to being them together again.

title: Aakhri Yudh
subTitle: After her family forces her to get married, Kavya runs away from her house. When her brother goes in search of her, he finds her with a young man and assumes him to be her boyfriend.

title: Ram Setu
subTitle: An atheist archaeologist turned believer races against time to prove the true existence of the legendary Ram Setu before evil forces destroy the pillar of India's heritage.

title: Hungama
subTitle: A trio in love triangle, a couple from the countryside, a disgruntled crime lord, and a myriad of other eccentric characters dance to a cacophony of reckless lies and misunderstandings.

title: Bholaa Shankar
subTitle: While trying to rebuild his life in Calcutta with his sister, a cab driver must face his dark past and the city's crime.

title: The Return of Abhimanyu
subTitle: A soldier takes on a gang of cyber criminals when money goes missing from his account.

title: The Return of Abhimanyu
subTitle: A soldier takes on a gang of cyber criminals when money goes missing from his account.

title: International Khiladi: The Iron Man
subTitle: Amrita's parents get killed. Years later, she falls in love with Aditya only to learn that he was the one who was accused of her parents' murder.

title: Colors Cineplex
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Karkash
subTitle: A wayward husband vows to punish his dutiful wife after a false rumour spreads in society that questions her fidelity. Eventually, the woman must take dire measures to prove her loyalty and honour.

title: Yuvaraj
subTitle: Yuva enrols in an engineering college after getting banned from his sport and picks up fights with local students. However, his life gets more strained when his father flees, owing a huge debt.

title: Conjuring Kannappan
subTitle: After clumsily plucking feathers off a spooky dreamcatcher, a family finds itself in a nightmarish realm where injuries and death manifest in reality.

title: Express Khiladi
subTitle: A pantry worker and a make-up artist develop a romance aboard a runaway train, where they must confront dangerous challenges to save themselves and others.

title: Vivegam
subTitle: A former counter-terrorism agent sets out to exact revenge on the friends who betray him and work for a secret agency.

title: Pichaikkaran
subTitle: A rich businessman's mother becomes comatose after she meets with an accident and the doctors are unable to cure her. However, a priest promises him that she would recover if he lives a beggar's life.

title: Rajini The Jailer
subTitle: A retired jailer lives a peaceful life with his family. But when his son, who is a policeman, goes missing and is supposedly killed, he is forced to go back to his world of crime and find the killer.

title: Petta
subTitle: A look at the secrets guarded by Kaali, who works as a humble hostel warden. When Kaali crosses paths with a group of dangerous gangsters, things take an interesting turn.

title: Petta
subTitle: A look at the secrets guarded by Kaali, who works as a humble hostel warden. When Kaali crosses paths with a group of dangerous gangsters, things take an interesting turn.

title: Deewar Man of Power
subTitle: Bujji and Chitti are good childhood friends, but after a fall-out Chitti asks Bujji not to see her again for 12 years, however, she promises to marry him after this time. Bujji then goes to live in Chennai and becomes a 'goonda'.

title: Cakewalk
subTitle: A young woman who works as a chef faces various challenges as she tries to maintain a balance between her personal and professional commitments.

title: Pappu Can't Dance Saala
subTitle: Fighting neighbours are forced to share the same apartment. They decide to go their own way, but meet up again after realising that they miss each other.

title: Time Machine
subTitle: When Elango and Pulivetti find a time machine, they decide to use it for their benefit. While meddling with time, they prevent a gangster's death and this lands them in trouble.

title: Raja Huli
subTitle: Raja agrees to help a friend convey his love to a woman and is surprised to find out it is his ex-girlfriend. When she falls for Raja again, an unfortunate series of events follows.

title: Kali Kitaab
subTitle: When narratives from a cryptic book spring to life, a woman experiences bizarre phenomena and resolves to uncover the identity of its enigmatic writer.

title: Daaku Maharaaj
subTitle: A daring robber, striving for survival and establishing his own territory amid conflicts with powerful adversaries, battling to become a "king without a kingdom."

title: DD Returns

title: Rudhran
subTitle: A man's life takes an unexpected turn when he stumbles upon a criminal network. Determined to bring the truth to light, he sets out to expose the organisation and protect his loved ones.

title: The Masterpiece
subTitle: Yuva beats up a drug lord while trying to help the woman he loves and faces various threats aimed at his family.
